{
  "stem": "21812.5",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I went back-- at that point I said to myself, I'm going back because I want to enjoy myself and I want to do things that I'd never done as a child there, had not been able to do.",
      "word_count": 39
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And that's what I did.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And we had a very good time.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "When I-- the only unpleasant experience was when we went to a place called Bad Ischl, a spa outside of Salzburg.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And she went into a shop there, looking at handbags.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And I was waiting outside.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And there was a couple, an Orthodox couple, came walking down the street.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And she wore a sheitel and he wore a black hat but no payos And-- but it was very obvious that-- nobody in the summertime wore hats there.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "It was obvious they were Jewish and a child with them.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And I was standing there, and I was sort of amazed that they were there, because it was my first time back.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I said, why would anybody who is really Orthodox want to come here?",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And then I saw an Austrian woman, elderly woman, giving them sort of dirty looks, and walking by and giving them dirty looks.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And I-- at that moment, I felt if anything had-- if anybody had said anything to them or anything had been done to them, I said, I could kill.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I could really kill.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And that was the feeling I had.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I-- nothing happened.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "She just looked at them and they walked by.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But that was the only time.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Otherwise, you know, I speak the language, and everybody was very pleasant.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "The second time, when Sylvia and I went there, Sylvia didn't like the place.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I didn't like it as much either.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
